  "application": "DLRM",

    "software": [

    "resources": {
      "hardware": "DGX system",

        "/workspace/dlrm/"

      "environment": {
        "DGXSYSTEM": "required",
        "CONT": "required",
        "NEXP": "optional, default: 5",
        "DATESTAMP": "optional, default: current date and time",
        "CLEAR_CACHES": "optional, default: 1",
        "MOUNTS": "optional, default: '/raid/datasets:/raid/datasets,/gpfs/fs1:/gpfs/fs1'",
        "LOGDIR": "optional, default: './results'",
        "DLRM_BIND": "optional, default: null"
      }
    }
  }
}
